<name>ENGINE</name>
<section id="1000C_S000L" variety="S000L">
<name>2AZ-FE COOLING</name>
<ttl id="1000C_S000L_7307R_T00EU" variety="T00EU">
<name>WATER PUMP</name>
<para id="RM0000017W8005X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="CO0AS-06" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM0000017W8005X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000017W8005X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00009Q900000">
<ptxt>INSPECT WATER PUMP ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Visually check the drain hole and air hole for coolant leakage.</ptxt>
<ptxt>If leakage is found, replace the water pump assembly.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A128603E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Turn the pulley, and then check that the water pump bearing moves smoothly without making a "click" sound.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A112198" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>If it does not move smoothly, replace the water pump assembly.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
</pub>
